des: This is a trivia about Indian cities and various information related to it. It's a fun trivia which checks your knowledge about India and it's cities. This can be used for fun and education/knowledge purpose. The quiz asks you questions about Indian cities, famous monuments in India, places of interest in Indian cities, historical sites in India, Indian cities geography etc. It's a light-weight app which can run smoothly on basic hardware. It's one of a kind trivia made specifically to enhance your knowledge about India and it's cities.
